user.canProvide: I'm always happy to chat with folks solving important problems in education or grappling with the challenges of engineering leadership!
user.greeting: I care about improving access to effective, equitable learning experiences.
user.intro: Over the past decade, I've built software responsible for millions of learning outcomes and tens of millions of dollars in revenue. My thoughts on career development, education technology, and engineering management have been shared in publications like TEDx, LeadDev, Developer Week, and EdSurge. I've led an engineering org from first employee through acquisition and have a patent pending for our work there.
user.lookingFor: I scout for Reach Capital, my personal favorite education-focused VC fund. If you're working on something in or adjacent to education, I'd love to chat!
